19 WHEREAS, Shawn Lane, Mayor of the City of Yellville, passed away on
20 April 4, 2025; and
21
22 WHEREAS, Shawn Lane was born on May 25, 1969, in Yellville, Arkansas,
23 the son of Charlie and Madelyn Carlton; and
24
25 WHEREAS, Shawn Lane was a 1987 graduate of Yellville-Summit High School
26 and received his Associate of Arts degree from North Arkansas College; and
27
28 WHEREAS, Shawn Lane married his beloved, Tonya Blair, on December 4,
29 1993, and two (2) wonderful daughters, McKenzi and Ryleigh, were born of the
30 marriage; and
31
32 WHEREAS, Shawn Lane worked for Yelcot Communications for thirty-four
33 (34) years, beginning as a part-time employee in 1991 and finishing as Vice
34 President of Operations; and
35
36 WHEREAS, Shawn Lane was also a fixture in Marion County community
